WEBVTT

00:05:59.275 --> 00:06:03.732
ya aidha kudhoofisha au kuzuia kabisa
udhibiti mkubwa wa usiri kwenye taarifa

00:06:03.756 --> 00:06:05.936
kwasababu watu wabaya wanautumia pia

00:06:06.465 --> 00:06:10.725
Tunatakiwa tupiganie haki ya wananchi
kutumia udhibiti mkubwa wa usiri.

00:06:10.749 --> 00:06:14.379
ama sivyo, upinzani na
uandishi wa habari za uchunguzi

00:06:14.403 --> 00:06:16.802
utapelekea kuwa na ugumu zaidi

00:06:16.826 --> 00:06:18.290
katika sehemu nyingi zaidi.

00:06:18.654 --> 00:06:21.125
na watu wabaya--wahalifu
na magaidi--

00:06:21.149 --> 00:06:23.409
bado wataendelea kutafuta
njia za kuwasiliana

00:06:23.433 --> 00:06:26.072
Pongezi kwa makampuni
ambayo yanasimamia

00:06:26.096 --> 00:06:28.550
haki ya watumiaji wake kutumia usiri

00:06:29.595 --> 00:06:31.861
Lakini inapokuja kwenye udhibiti,